node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Scary Mommy on August 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'When you lose your shit after a long day and your kid gives you this face so now you have to take them to get ice cream and start shopping for ponies to make up for it: Mominy Hưôeg Scary'.

Photo by Scary Mommy on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'My son just asked me if we can cut his eyelashes because they hit the top of his goggles when he swims. I think we have a new definition of the phrase "not fucking fair." Scary'.

Photo shared by Scary Mommy on August 17, 2021 tagging @chasten.buttigieg. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'Pete Buttigieg @PeteButtigieg For some time, Chasten and I have wanted to to grow our family. We're overjoyed to share that we've become parents! The process isn't done yet and we're thankful for the love, support, and respect for our privacy that has been offered to us. We can't wait to share more soon.'.

Photo by Scary Mommy on August 17, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Usually the Olympics are about watching obscure sports once every 4 years, but this year the key takeaways were mental health advocacy, calling out sexualization of women's competition suits, and reform for marijuana laws. That's an Olympics we can get behind! Scary'.

Photo shared by Scary Mommy on August 17, 2021 tagging @cerealonthefloor. May be an image of text that says 'Cereal on the Floor @cerealonfloor Just refilling my kids' water bottles for the third time today and thinking about how I didn't drink a glass of water my entire childhood.'.
